  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "We stand at a pivotal moment in human history: our technologies have never been more powerful, nor our ecological crises more dire. While the Industrial and Digital Revolutions granted us vast capabilities to reshape the planet, they also brought pollution, biodiversity loss, and profound socio-environmental disruptions. Yet humanity is on the cusp of another renaissance — a regenaissance — one that harnesses artificial intelligence and regenerative economics to fund and catalyze real-world projects focusing on planetary healing. We need collaborative synergistic solutions, building out a web for a planetary-scale coordination system that can unite regenerative efforts across bioregions at scale.",
